  <section>
    <h2>Turn-by-Turn Directions üó∫Ô∏è</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Start at Via Borgo Giannotti 19, Lucca</li>
      <li>Follow Serchio River Path east (~10 km)</li>
      <li>Cross Ponte a Moriano, continue on Via di Poggio to Capannori</li>
      <li>Take Via delle Ville through olive groves</li>
      <li>Join Via Francigena trail toward Altopascio</li>
      <li>Follow Via Romana Vecchia to Fucecchio</li>
      <li><strong>Lunch Stop:</strong> Ristorante La Buca or Osteria del Gambero Rosso</li>
      <li>Continue via Via di Burello to Cerreto Guidi</li>
      <li>Ride Via di Monterappoli into Empoli</li>
      <li>Finish at Piazza Don Minzoni 18</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

